    <div class="content"><p>[textile]<br />
"Do they feel cheated with a letterbox movie on a 4:3 TV?"<br />
Yes, yes they do.  These are the people who buy pan &amp; scan "full screen" DVDs instead of widescreen.</p>
</div>
