    <div class="content"><p>Most DVD players have this feature. At least they do here in the UK, and I'd be surprised if they don't in the US. (Look for a 4:3 Pan &amp; Scan option in the player's setup menu.) But the feature is useless because DVD makers never put the necessary "vector" data on the DVDs.</p>
